## Learning Journey
### The Stamford Arts Centre Digital Experience

###### _#Digitalise #Engage_

re you curious how traditional arts and technology are used to engage the masses? Visit the Stamford Arts Centre where you get to experience a virtual reality Chinese Opera Stage tour and an augmented reality Stamford Arts Centre Walking Trail to find out how the way NAC engages citizens have shifted. 

**Date and Time: 9 July (Tue), 3.00pm - 5.00pm** <br>

**Location: Stamford Arts Centre, 155 Waterloo Streeet S(187962)** <br>

**Indicate Your Interest [here](https://www.eventbrite.sg/e/step-into-my-shoes-making-a-difference-as-a-probation-officer-tickets-61082209533)** 

